OL,7,FBath and North East Somerset Council
OL,8,Fhas warned traders they could face
OL,9,Fcourt action if they sell illegal
OL,10,Fvaping products, or sell to underage
OL,11,Fbuyers.
OL,13,FIt follows the prosecution of three
OL,14,Ftraders by the council's Trading
OL,15,FStandards Department.
OL,17,FMagistrates heard how a 15-year-old
OL,18,Fvolunteer working with the council's
OL,19,FTrading Standards team was sold the
OL,20,Fproducts in August last year.
