OL,7,FIt is illegal to sell vapes and e-
OL,8,Fcigarettes to anyone under the age of
OL,9,F18.
OL,11,FBrian Ede, owner of Rings and Things
OL,12,Fmarket stall in Green Park Station,
OL,13,Fand Poonnambalam Murali, owner of the
OL,14,FCostcutter and PKT Stores in ,
OL,15,Fadmitted selling vaping products to
OL,16,Funder 18s.
OL,18,FEde was fined #108 for the offence and
OL,19,Fordered to pay costs totalling #750
OL,20,Fand a victim surcharge of #43 after
OL,21,Fthe sale from his premises.
