OL,7,FFollowing sales to the volunteer at
OL,8,Fboth of his premises, Murali was fined
OL,9,F#322 for each offence and ordered to
OL,10,Fpay costs of #1569 and a victim
OL,11,Fsurcharge of #250.
OL,13,FYuvi Private Limited, which runs
OL,14,FBishop Sutton Post Office, also
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty to offences under the
OL,16,FNicotine Inhaling Products (Age of
OL,17,FSale and Proxy Purchasing) Regulations
OL,18,F2015.
