OL,7,FAt the post office, officers
OL,8,Fadditionally found vapes for sale
OL,9,Fwhich contained nicotine liquid in
OL,10,Fquantities above the two millilitre
OL,11,Flegally allowed limit.
OL,13,FThe illegal vapes were seized. Yuvi
OL,14,FPrivate Limited pleaded guilty to this
OL,15,Foffence under the Tobacco and Related
OL,16,FProducts Regulations 2016 and the
OL,17,Fmagistrates ordered the illegal vapes
OL,18,Fbe forfeited and destroyed.
