OL,7,FYuvi Private Limited was fined #160
OL,8,Ffor the underage sales offence and
OL,9,F#484 for the sale of the illegal
OL,10,Fvapes. They were ordered to pay #1781
OL,11,Fcosts and a victim surcharge of #260.
OL,13,FCouncillor Tim Ball, cabinet member
OL,14,Ffor neighbourhood services, said: "Our
OL,15,FTrading Standards team is working hard
OL,16,Fto stop vapes being made available to
OL,17,Funder 18s.
