OL,7,F"Our test purchasing exercise showed
OL,8,Fthat most traders in our area are
OL,9,Fcomplying with the law and did not
OL,10,Fsell to our underage volunteer which
OL,11,Fis good news, however we will continue
OL,12,Fto make checks on retailers that sell
OL,13,Fvapes so we can protect consumers from
OL,14,Fillegal activity and products."
OL,16,FAnyone concerned about illegal, or
OL,17,Funderage sales of age-restricted goods
OL,18,Fshould report it to Trading Standards
OL,19,Fvia the Citizens Advice Consumer
OL,20,FService helpline on 0808 223 1133.
